author = ALEXANDRE HENEFFE 



Istructions and Specifications of how to compile, 
install and execute the PSO implementation and configure the robot swarm controller:
=====================================================================================================

- the language used is Python3 so just install python3 and the following libraries : 

    - required python Libraries : 
        - time
        - math
        - threading
        - csv
        - random
        - datetime
        - ranksums from scipy.stats
        - subprocess
        - shlex

        
=====================================================================================================
- to run the PSO : 

    - first manually set the random seeds in the 10 different decision-making{i}.argos where i is between 1 and 10
    
    - change the seeds in the main() function of main.py
    
    - then, run "python3 main.py" in terminal
    
- The results are shown in terminal and the csv + boxplots files are created in the "Results" file


=====================================================================================================

Explanation of Files : 
    in Code : 
        - decision-making1.argos to decision-making10.argos are used for the multiple runs of PSO with threads. Each argos file has a different seed that is the same as the PSO's seed
        - decision-making.argos has a random seed in it
        - pso_solution1.lua to pso_solution10.lua are used by the decision-making1.argos to decision-making10.argos, respectively
        - the pso_solution.lua is used by decision-making.argos
        - simulation_parameters1.txt to simulation_parameters10.txt are used to store solutions parameters (velocity, etc..) and are used by the pso_solution files
        - simulation_parameters.txt is used by pso_solution.lua 
        
        - decision-making_test.argos is here to test the ultimate solution found by 10 PSO  or the manual solution
        - decision-making_visual.argos is here to visualize an argos experiment.
        - manual_solution.lua is the lua file of the initial controller solution (before pso)
    
    

